Sentencas: Developing low-polarization and stable cathodes is key to the success of intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Performance and stability of SrCo0.9Nb0.1O3-δ-(La0.60Sr0.40)0.95(Co0.20Fe0.80)O3-δ bilayer cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Here we report a study on the electrochemical performance and stability of a commercial (La0.60Sr0.40)(0.95)(Co0.20Fe0.80)O3-delta (LSCF) cathode overcoated by a SrCo0.0Nb0.1O3-delta (SCN10) nanoscaled layer.
Titulo: Performance and stability of SrCo0.9Nb0.1O3-δ-(La0.60Sr0.40)0.95(Co0.20Fe0.80)O3-δ bilayer cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At the optimal 20 wt% loading, the SCN10-LSCF bilayer cathode exhibits an 89.4% reduction in polarization resistance over the pristine LSCF at 650 degrees C.
Titulo: Performance and stability of SrCo0.9Nb0.1O3-δ-(La0.60Sr0.40)0.95(Co0.20Fe0.80)O3-δ bilayer cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Over a 6,000-h testing at 650 degrees C, the SCN10-LSCF bilayer cathode also shows a similar stability to but much lower resistance than the pristine LSCF.
Titulo: Performance and stability of SrCo0.9Nb0.1O3-δ-(La0.60Sr0.40)0.95(Co0.20Fe0.80)O3-δ bilayer cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A combined microscopic and spectroscopic post-test analysis unveils that SCN10-overcoat remains nanosized, well crystallized and uniformly distributed.
Titulo: Performance and stability of SrCo0.9Nb0.1O3-δ-(La0.60Sr0.40)0.95(Co0.20Fe0.80)O3-δ bilayer cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: An elongated, sporadically distributed phase was found and identified as SrCO3 in the SCN10 layer, which may contribute to the degradation of SCN10-LSCF cathode.
Titulo: Performance and stability of SrCo0.9Nb0.1O3-δ-(La0.60Sr0.40)0.95(Co0.20Fe0.80)O3-δ bilayer cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
